  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/7dfab1c0d043a7640d60796765ba39b7.avif?t=1654676926\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Previously under the title of <u>SYNDER</u>.<br><br>T̤̦̰̟͉̰̔͐ͫ͘ͅͅh̜̝̭̥̮ͩ̔ͬ̚͟ę̥̯͓̣ͧ͗ͧ ̯̗̝͇̮̗͉̒̍͘D̷͚̙̖͎̖̥͖̣̃̓̑ę̖̰ͣ͑a͍͖͚̤̬ͥ́͆̄͞d̵͕̻̜͚͍̻̱ͯ ͉̞͔̌ͯͩ̾́R̶̬͉͍̭̰̰̻͐ò͇͖̪̫͚̤̹͍̽ͯ͡ő̵͈͍̦͇͔̦m̢̗͉ͥ͊̂s̘̘͕̲̙͙͕͉͋̇͋̓͢ have taken you. Push through, what seems as an enigmatic living dimension extending randomly for eternity.<br><br><br>Experience dread and isolation as you navigate a seemingly endless realm of rooms, search for supplies/weapons and maintain your sanity as you hope for an exit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IT'S LIKE THE FIRST TIME, EVERYTIME!</h2>The Dead Rooms is ever evolving and adapting, Every run will feature different rooms and layouts + loot, and offer a different playthrough<br>Sometime you may get lucky..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/65b543ac1a22718279cc7e36a9b9487b.poster.avif?t=1654676926\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/65b543ac1a22718279cc7e36a9b9487b.webm?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/65b543ac1a22718279cc7e36a9b9487b.mp4?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO MORE WALKING SIMULATORS!</h2>The Dead Rooms aims to be an <strong>actually game</strong>, not just an immersive experience. Featuring survival and roguelite mechanics such as character management and <strong>perma death</strong> with the chance to find your previous body on your next run!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL VARIETY!</h2>As you progress further, The Dead Rooms will feature a variety of rooms featured in The Back Rooms Lore, more being added after release! <br><strong>Below are planned with more on the way!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level 0 - \"The Lobby\"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/5eaf73144421fb87b45ba6f6b6d34412.poster.avif?t=1654676926\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/5eaf73144421fb87b45ba6f6b6d34412.webm?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/5eaf73144421fb87b45ba6f6b6d34412.mp4?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level 427 - \"Infinite Mall\"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/df2708734bac6441d2b9640f093981f7.poster.avif?t=1654676926\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/df2708734bac6441d2b9640f093981f7.webm?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/df2708734bac6441d2b9640f093981f7.mp4?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level 239 - \"Infinite Arcade\"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/311e964d30b22d4feec2c7a3d2ba7347.poster.avif?t=1654676926\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/311e964d30b22d4feec2c7a3d2ba7347.webm?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687130/extras/311e964d30b22d4feec2c7a3d2ba7347.mp4?t=1654676926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level 974 - \"Kitty's House\"</h2></li></ul>",
